  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/203e1bf6ac26a344a38ee6f8378c3e02.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/203e1bf6ac26a344a38ee6f8378c3e02.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>Interact with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. Crack enigmas and collect hidden puzzle tiles on a random side of the boxes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/7eed6ea13caf9611d40cd5f6d43c6b6f.poster.avif?t=1751521328\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/7eed6ea13caf9611d40cd5f6d43c6b6f.webm?t=1751521328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/7eed6ea13caf9611d40cd5f6d43c6b6f.mp4?t=1751521328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/9bcdf064d3b1b16b26fe07d6487e858d.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/9bcdf064d3b1b16b26fe07d6487e858d.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>You won't be able to compare reality with fiction!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/da832725d526e6a5b7442c9a7274e007.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/da832725d526e6a5b7442c9a7274e007.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>Once you unlock all 8 boxes of a Level Pack, you can compose a puzzle and discover a brief history of an invention.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/45ee3f27564752c14777323af6b165ce.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/45ee3f27564752c14777323af6b165ce.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>It's not always easy to escape the room, so use all your IQ to crack the riddles. There's a logic behind all of them, even where it seems it's not!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/b54494906863b391f73d89d53e1efc9d.poster.avif?t=1751521328\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/b54494906863b391f73d89d53e1efc9d.webm?t=1751521328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/b54494906863b391f73d89d53e1efc9d.mp4?t=1751521328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/473c2896ca5cc34fc747b9a0cbe0218c.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/473c2896ca5cc34fc747b9a0cbe0218c.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>Play the game with your headphones to get immersed in this amazing adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/e0940c28db3c10e03bf930fa2a72fd0d.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/e0940c28db3c10e03bf930fa2a72fd0d.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>Got stuck on some enigma? No worries, you can still get a helpful hint! You can also get in touch with me in case you really can't make it through a riddle, I'll be glad to help ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/6b319dc951e046fab0f6b330c6d5306e.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/6b319dc951e046fab0f6b330c6d5306e.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>Available in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>*The game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/203e1bf6ac26a344a38ee6f8378c3e02.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/203e1bf6ac26a344a38ee6f8378c3e02.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>Interact with objects, handles, buttons, and wheels on each side. Crack enigmas and collect hidden puzzle tiles on a random side of the boxes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/7eed6ea13caf9611d40cd5f6d43c6b6f.poster.avif?t=1751521328\" width=614 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/7eed6ea13caf9611d40cd5f6d43c6b6f.webm?t=1751521328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/7eed6ea13caf9611d40cd5f6d43c6b6f.mp4?t=1751521328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/9bcdf064d3b1b16b26fe07d6487e858d.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/9bcdf064d3b1b16b26fe07d6487e858d.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>You won't be able to compare reality with fiction!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/da832725d526e6a5b7442c9a7274e007.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shar