e game with your headphones to get immersed in this amazing adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/e0940c28db3c10e03bf930fa2a72fd0d.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/e0940c28db3c10e03bf930fa2a72fd0d.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>Got stuck on some enigma? No worries, you can still get a helpful hint! You can also get in touch with me in case you really can't make it through a riddle, I'll be glad to help ;)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/6b319dc951e046fab0f6b330c6d5306e.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/6b319dc951e046fab0f6b330c6d5306e.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span>Available in English, French, Italian, German, Spanish, Russian, and Japanese.*</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>*The game language will change automatically based on the language settings of your device </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i></i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521328\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2738770/extras_big/0052aef59fd35355bd4d7a4e808fe547.avif?t=1751521328 width=800 height=212 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hi there, <strong>Frank Eno</strong>'s here, I have been creating escape room and puzzle games since 2020 under the name of  <strong>XSGames</strong>, doing all by myself: code, graphics, music, design, concept, etc.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong><i>If you like my works, consider leaving a review here on Steam, your support will be greatly appreciated!</i></strong></p>",
